the thing I love most about motherhood , is that my kids help me heal . I am able to see different parts of myself in them , & they are helping me heal the deepest parts of myself that I didn’t even know needed healing . no one says how much having children heals your inner child ♥️ 

it is so important to show love to your younger self 
& to let them know they are safe , loved & protected 

you can’t change the past or the circumstances you were in , but you can heal in the now 

try saying these words to your own inner child within you 

you are  safe
you are loved 
you are protected 
you are enough 
you are worthy
you are beautiful 
you are seen 
you are valued 

don’t forget 

✨✨✨

.
.
.
